****************In order to run the Autonomous mode in the Simulator*********************

The projects zip file contains the python code , jupiter notebook and the environment we activate to launch the code on 

Steps :
#1: Open Linux_Roverism 
#2: Click on  Roverismx86_64 
#2: click on Ok
#3: Unzip Vision Project File 
#4: click on vision project folder 
#5: click on code folder 
#6: open in terminal 
#7: in terminal , type : 1. conda activate vision-project
                         2. python drive_rover.py
#8: click on Autonomous mode from the Roverismx86_64 tab 

